To make 'Join'

(1) Copy the contents of this disc to a suitable location on a hard disc
(2) Ensure that cc and Link are on the run path
(3) Delete $.Join (the final image) if it exists
(4) Delete $.o.Join if it exists
(5) Double click on $.DoMake

All the necessary tools and libraries ($.OSLib.o.oslib and $.CLib.o.Stubs)
are contained on this disc, apart cc and Link.

The versions of cc and link used with all this are on the
floppy containing extract 2.19 sources.